01:52.132 --> 01:55.334
- Just because we dress nice,
doesn't mean we're spoiled.

01:55.334 --> 01:57.575
- They are definitely
a little bit spoiled.

01:59.098 --> 02:00.829
- [Gordon] Rina's not
just a little bit spoiled,

02:00.829 --> 02:02.758
