03:36.888 --> 03:39.399
- Oh, that's mouldy.
- Oh, man.

03:42.931 --> 03:43.799
- Look at this!

03:43.799 --> 03:44.675
How are your allergies doing?

03:44.675 --> 03:46.552
- They're a little bit rough.

03:47.683 --> 03:48.867
- Do you need your inhaler?

03:49.875 --> 03:51.752
- [Gordon] With almost
no guests coming in,

03:51.752 --> 03:53.504
