10:51.540 --> 10:55.176
- It's so hard Gordon
to just repeat myself.

10:55.176 --> 10:56.458
- But I'm not so sure.

10:56.458 --> 10:57.720
- She wasn't gone for two weeks,

10:57.720 --> 10:59.284
